msgctxt "984"
msgid "Chatty Businesswoman"
msgstr "Mujer de negocios habladora"

msgctxt "988"
msgid "Reserved Businesswoman"
msgstr "Mujer de negocios reservada"

msgctxt "992"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "996"
msgid "Talk_Quest"
msgstr "Talk_Quest"

msgctxt "84_Chatty Businesswoman"
msgid "Doesn't it seem like there are more... thugs around town?"
msgstr "¿No parece que hay más... matones por la ciudad?"

msgctxt "96_Reserved Businesswoman"
msgid "Hm? I haven't noticed."
msgstr "¿Mm? No me he dado cuenta."

msgctxt "108_Chatty Businesswoman"
msgid "Well there totally are! People like that usually stick to\\r\n"
"shadows, yet here they are roaming around in broad daylight!"
msgstr "¡Pues definitivamente los hay! Gente así suele quedarse\\r\n"
"en las sombras, ¡pero están aquí paseandose por la ciudad\\r\n"
"a plena luz del día!"

msgctxt "120_Chatty Businesswoman"
msgid "I wonder if something's going on. Kamurocho is usually so\\r\n"
"safe and quiet, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132_Reserved Businesswoman"
msgid "Is it, though...?"
msgstr "¿Pero... lo es de verdad?"

